column4: <content>Ad [Addendum] 33. Ad Cripples, Louvre. Witt Library, in Box Bruegel I, Box 4: Last in folder. Outdoor Genre Weddings...Without Bridal [onleesbaar]... Sale Drouot, Paris 27 Jan. 1921. BRVEGHEL, le Drôle, Peter. 14. Jour de Fête dans les Flandres [...]; [verso] [...] (three cripples with fox-tails) [...]; [toegevoegde vermelding]: 'F.G. Late XVI C. with the three cripples is a woman like in B's picture. But in B.'s picture it is summer, here winter.'</content>
